---
/**
 * Testimonial - 4.9/5 Trusted by genius people
 */
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-dark-700 bg-dark-900">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl text-accent font-bold mb-4">4.9/5</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-8">Trusted by genius people.</h2>
    <blockquote class="text-white/70 text-lg italic mb-8">
      "Working with was an outstanding experience."
    </blockquote>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-2">
      {[1, 2, 3].map((i) => (
        <span class:list={['w-2 h-2 rounded-full', i === 1 ? 'bg-accent' : 'bg-white/30']}></span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
